hopobject.body: How do I get an outside line? fenumass bodybuilding Income inequality is the bane of our current economic system, or should I say, how we do capitalism. Excellent piece, by the way. You’re shining a light on a huge problem that is guaranteed to transform the US into something the world has never quite seen before, and it isn’t good. It’s not exactly a “third world economy,” but increasingly our economy is sharing many of the detrimental characteristics of a third world economy starting with, of course, extreme income inequality.
